name: HARD LANDING! Cargolux 747-467F [LX-ICL] Windy Arrival at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Thanks to a powerful low pressure system from the west, we had some crazy winds in Calgary today! This led to some very interesting arrivals with huge wind gusts, causing quite a few go-arounds. One of the more special arrivals was this Cargolux 747-400 in a basic Cathay Pacific livery which made a very hard and early touchdown on 35L in some perfect lighting between clouds. If you've seen some of my other videos from this spot, you'll see that aircraft touchdown much further, just before the ILS mast comes into view. In this case, they touched down right on the runway numbers! Hope you enjoy this spectacular windy landing, with ATC included.

Thanks for watching!
